txt.en: You have been tasked with guarding Trader's Wharf from potential threats.
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Radhril for your reward!

'Would you accompany me on a mission, [placeholder]?

'The League of the Axe has reached out to me, asking for assistance in guarding Trader's Wharf while the League departs for an important mission.

'The League of the Axe is respectful of the lands. I would like to assist them, however I would need your assistance.'
Complete Mission: Trouble on the Brandywine
Those of Trader's Wharf have all been called away, and you are the only one left to defend the docks from attackers.\n\nYour mission is to guard Trader's Wharf from potential threats.
Monsters in this mission will enrage at low morale, gaining attack strength and attack speed.
Your mission is to guard Trader's Wharf from potential threats.\n\nSpeak to Radhril.
'We have done well, [placeholder]. With Trader's Wharf still standing from the brigand assault, the League of the Axe will certainly be thankful of our efforts.'
